<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 30 at 6:25AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Patchy Freezing Drizzle Possible This Morning...
Patchy freezing drizzle may occur in some parts of the Capital
District, Helderbergs, Mohawk Valley and Saratoga region into
this morning. Some locally slippery spots may develop, especially
on untreated ground surfaces, as well as on bridges and elevated
roadways. Motorists are urged to use caution.</description>
